627
00:44:46,533 --> 00:44:47,866
♫ Across tens of thousands of miles, ♫

628
00:44:48,233 --> 00:44:49,666
♫ who is the one crossing the waves with me, ♫

629
00:44:50,000 --> 00:44:53,233
♫ with our hearts unrepentant,
