630
00:44:53,433 --> 00:44:54,866
♫ Across tens of thousands of miles, ♫

631
00:44:55,133 --> 00:44:56,666
♫ oceans and lands witness that♫

632
00:44:56,900 --> 00:44:59,666
♫ the world will be safe and sound. ♫

633
00:45:00,066 --> 00:45:03,100
♫ Across tens of thousands of miles, ♫

